{"id": "题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2", "name": "_1442__gpt5.4_mini__sample_2", "description": "", "category": "gui", "query": "", "steps": [{"id": 0, "action_type": "wait", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/1.webp", "action_value_1": [], "thought": "我先看到的是Ubuntu桌面，还没有打开OpenPLC Editor。下一步我会启动软件，进入新建项目流程，然后按题目要求配置LD梯形图和变量。"}, {"id": 1, "action_type": "hotkey", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/2.webp", "action_value_1": ["ctrl alt t"], "thought": "桌面上能看到目标相关文件夹，但还没进入编辑器。我先打开终端，用给定脚本启动OpenPLC Editor，这样可以直接进入项目创建。"}, {"id": 2, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/3.webp", "action_value_1": "Terminal", "thought": "快捷键没有明显弹出终端，我改用系统搜索打开Terminal，再执行启动脚本。这样更稳妥，也不影响后面建项目。"}, {"id": 3, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/4.webp", "action_value_1": "sh ", "thought": "终端已经打开，刚才多出来的“Terminal”只是误输入，不影响。现在直接执行启动脚本，等编辑器窗口出现。"}, {"id": 4, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/5.webp", "action_value_1": "ls -R ", "thought": "脚本路径报错，说明实际文件名或目录层级和题目描述略有差别。我先在Downloads里查找OpenPLC Editor的真实路径，再按找到的路径启动。"}, {"id": 5, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/6.webp", "action_value_1": "ls ", "thought": "我已经确认Downloads里确实有OpenPLC相关目录，只是路径名称不同。下一步我直接查看顶层目录名，找到真正的启动脚本位置。"}, {"id": 6, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/7.webp", "action_value_1": "find ", "thought": "现在已经确认下载目录里是 `OpenPLC_Editor`，不是题面写法。接下来我会在该目录下精准查找启动脚本名，然后直接运行它。"}, {"id": 7, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/8.webp", "action_value_1": "sh ", "thought": "已经找到正确脚本 `openplc_editor.sh`。现在启动OpenPLC Editor，进入后我就开始新建项目和编写梯形图。"}, {"id": 8, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/9.webp", "action_value_1": "sed -n ", "thought": "脚本用 `sh` 直接跑出现了解释器和路径问题，说明它需要在正确目录下并且更适合用 bash 启动。我先看看脚本头部，确认启动方式，然后用正确命令重试。"}, {"id": 9, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/10.webp", "action_value_1": "ls ", "thought": "脚本头部已经说明真正的工作目录是 `OpenPLC Editor for Linux/OpenPLC_Editor`，而且它要用自带的虚拟环境启动。接下来我切到那个目录再执行。"}, {"id": 10, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/11.webp", "action_value_1": "ls -l /home/user/Downloads/OpenPLC_Editor/OpenPLC_Editor/.venv/bin", "thought": "外层“OpenPLC Editor for Linux”目录并不存在，所以脚本里的 `cd` 目标失效了。最直接的办法是检查当前包里自己的 `.venv` 和启动文件，手工在正确目录运行编辑器。"}, {"id": 11, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/12.webp", "action_value_1": "cd /home/user/Downloads/OpenPLC_Editor/OpenPLC_Editor && ./.venv/bin/python3 ./editor/Beremiz.py", "thought": "`.venv` 和 `Beremiz.py` 都存在，所以不必再依赖那个错误的壳脚本。我直接在正确目录下用虚拟环境的 Python 启动主程序。"}, {"id": 12, "action_type": "wait", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/13.webp", "action_value_1": [], "thought": "编辑器正在启动，我先等待窗口加载完成。只要主界面出现，就立刻新建项目并按要求布置梯形图。"}, {"id": 13, "action_type": "hotkey", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/14.webp", "action_value_1": ["ctrl n"], "thought": "编辑器主界面已打开，左侧项目树还是空的。现在创建新项目最省事的是直接用新建命令，接着在向导里填项目名、路径和LD程序信息。"}, {"id": 14, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/15.webp", "action_value_1": [101, 109]}, {"id": 15, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/16.webp", "action_value_1": [359, 458], "thought": "现在弹出了“选择空目录”的对话框。题目要求把项目放到桌面 `output/Case1_Motor` 下，所以我先进入 Desktop，再进入 output 文件夹创建项目目录。"}, {"id": 16, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/17.webp", "action_value_1": [356, 225], "thought": "已经进入OpenPLC包目录了，但项目应该建在桌面的 `output` 里，不在安装包内。我现在切回左侧的 Desktop 入口，再进入 output 文件夹。"}, {"id": 17, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/18.webp", "action_value_1": [514, 277]}, {"id": 18, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/19.webp", "action_value_1": [1232, 147], "thought": "`output` 目录是空的，正适合作为工程母目录。现在我在里面新建 `Case1_Motor` 文件夹，然后把这个文件夹作为新项目目录。"}, {"id": 19, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/20.webp", "action_value_1": "Case1_Motor"}, {"id": 20, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/21.webp", "action_value_1": [1219, 103], "thought": "项目文件夹已经创建并进入了。下一步只要点 `Open`，就能以这个空目录创建新工程。"}, {"id": 21, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/22.webp", "action_value_1": "Main", "thought": "新工程已经建好，当前弹出的是创建 POU 的窗口。题目要求主程序名是 `Main`，语言是 `LD`，所以我把默认名字改掉并在语言里选梯形图。"}, {"id": 22, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/23.webp", "action_value_1": [862, 498]}, {"id": 23, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/24.webp", "action_value_1": [768, 592]}, {"id": 24, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/25.webp", "action_value_1": [170, 212], "thought": "工程和主程序都已经生成了，接下来我先打开 `Main` 的LD编辑区，再补变量表和梯形图逻辑。之后再检查工程名是否需要改成 `Case1_Motor`。"}, {"id": 25, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/26.webp", "action_value_1": [1112, 185], "thought": "已经进入 `Main` 的编辑页，梯形图区和变量表都可用。下一步先把三个 BOOL 变量加进表里，这样后面放触点和线圈时能直接引用。"}, {"id": 26, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/27.webp", "action_value_1": [1110, 183], "thought": "变量表还是空的，说明刚才没有点到真正的“添加变量”按钮。我再精确点击一次绿色加号，确认出现一行后再填写三条变量。"}, {"id": 27, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/28.webp", "action_value_1": [1108, 184], "thought": "已经成功插入了变量行，只是默认生成的是 `LocalVar0 / DINT`。我接下来继续加两行，再把三行分别改成题目要求的 `Start_PB`、`Stop_PB`、`Motor` 且类型都是 `BOOL`。"}, {"id": 28, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/29.webp", "action_value_1": [490, 256], "thought": "三条默认变量行已经都出来了。现在开始逐行改名和改类型：先把第一行改为 `Start_PB : BOOL`，再改第二行和第三行。"}, {"id": 29, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/30.webp", "action_value_1": "Start_PB"}, {"id": 30, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/31.webp", "action_value_1": [618, 254], "thought": "第一行名字已经改好，但类型还默认是 `DINT`。我继续把这一行的类型改为 `BOOL`，再把其余两行按同样方式修改。"}, {"id": 31, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/32.webp", "action_value_1": [757, 255], "thought": "类型下拉已经打开了，BOOL 属于基础类型。现在我从 `Base Types` 里面选 `BOOL`，把这一行改正确。"}, {"id": 32, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/33.webp", "action_value_1": [934, 257]}, {"id": 33, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/34.webp", "action_value_1": "Stop_PB"}, {"id": 34, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/35.webp", "action_value_1": [623, 281]}, {"id": 35, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/36.webp", "action_value_1": [763, 285]}, {"id": 36, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/37.webp", "action_value_1": [625, 281], "thought": "第二行类型还没改成功，说明上一步没有准确选中菜单项。我重新打开类型列表，并直接点最上面的 `BOOL`，把第二行固定改成布尔类型。"}, {"id": 37, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/38.webp", "action_value_1": "BOOL", "thought": "第二行的下拉选项比较难点中，我改用直接覆盖单元格文本的方式：选中 `DINT`，直接输入 `BOOL` 并回车，看是否能立即生效。"}, {"id": 38, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/39.webp", "action_value_1": [757, 285], "thought": "类型菜单还在展开状态，说明需要先悬停到 `Base Types` 触发右侧子菜单，再点 `BOOL`。我分两步慢一点操作，避免菜单消失。"}, {"id": 39, "action_type": "hotkey", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/40.webp", "action_value_1": ["b"], "thought": "单元格看起来已经处在可编辑状态，我试试用键盘直接输入 `B` 来利用下拉框的首字母搜索，看看能不能快速跳到 `BOOL`。"}, {"id": 40, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/41.webp", "action_value_1": "BOOL", "thought": "菜单一直卡着，我先用 `Esc` 收掉下拉框，再尝试对单元格直接输入 `BOOL`。这样如果编辑器支持文本覆盖，就能绕过菜单操作。"}, {"id": 41, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/42.webp", "action_value_1": [758, 286], "thought": "下拉框还没收掉，不过这正好说明它仍处于可交互状态。我把鼠标稳定悬停在 `Base Types` 上，等右侧子菜单展开后直接点 `BOOL`。"}, {"id": 42, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/43.webp", "action_value_1": [945, 284]}, {"id": 43, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/44.webp", "action_value_1": "Motor"}, {"id": 44, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/45.webp", "action_value_1": [623, 311], "thought": "第三行名称已经改成 `Motor`，还差类型 `BOOL`。我继续用前面成功的方法，把第三行的类型从 `DINT` 改成 `BOOL`。"}, {"id": 45, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/46.webp", "action_value_1": [629, 311], "thought": "第三行类型还没切换成功，所以我再重新触发一次下拉，并等待菜单完全展开后再点 `BOOL`。这次把动作放慢一点。"}, {"id": 46, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/47.webp", "action_value_1": [631, 310], "thought": "第三行我改用键盘快捷筛选：先激活类型单元格，然后直接按 `B` 再回车，看看下拉菜单是否会跳到 `BOOL`。"}, {"id": 47, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/48.webp", "action_value_1": [758, 314]}, {"id": 48, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/49.webp", "action_value_1": [628, 311], "thought": "我再做一次完整的菜单展开验证：先把第三行类型菜单打开，确认右侧子菜单真的出来后，再用鼠标点 `BOOL`。这样能排除坐标偏差。"}, {"id": 49, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/50.webp", "action_value_1": [943, 286]}, {"id": 50, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目