ct`。"}, {"id": 60, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/61.webp", "action_value_1": [742, 531], "thought": "接触点属性窗口出现了，现在把变量设为 `Start_PB`，并保持 `Normal` 常开状态。这样就是启动按钮。"}, {"id": 61, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/62.webp", "action_value_1": [681, 597]}, {"id": 62, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/63.webp", "action_value_1": [528, 412], "thought": "第一个 `Start_PB` 常开触点已经放好。现在我在它右侧继续接第二个触点，并把它设成 `Stop_PB` 的取反触点。"}, {"id": 63, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/64.webp", "action_value_1": [546, 411], "thought": "现在第一只触点右侧已经出现新的连接位置，我继续在这个位置插入第二个串联触点，用来放 `Stop_PB` 的取反常闭。"}, {"id": 64, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/65.webp", "action_value_1": [609, 479]}, {"id": 65, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/66.webp", "action_value_1": [741, 531], "thought": "第二个触点需要 `Stop_PB`，而且题目要求它是取反触点，所以我先选变量，再把修饰符改成 `Negated`。"}, {"id": 66, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/67.webp", "action_value_1": [685, 623]}, {"id": 67, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/68.webp", "action_value_1": [844, 574], "thought": "第二个触点已经改成 `Negated + Stop_PB`，和题目一致。现在确认插入。"}, {"id": 68, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/69.webp", "action_value_1": [588, 411], "thought": "串联的两个触点已经有了。现在我要在最右边继续放 `Motor` 线圈，并把右母线补上，使整条回路闭合。"}, {"id": 69, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/70.webp", "action_value_1": [641, 502]}, {"id": 70, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-mini-sample-2/71.webp", "action_value_1": [739, 531], "thought": "线圈属性窗口打开了，默认是普通线圈。现在把变量改成 `Motor`，这就是传送带电机输出。"}, {"id": 71, "action_type": "mo